title: Star Trek  Voyager Collection by Various Authors epub
description:
Star Trek - Voyager collection by Various Authors (41 Books)

Pocket Books was the first publisher given license by Paramount to produce a series of original novels and episode novelizations based on Star Trek: Voyager. All VOY novels and adaptations have been part of this ongoing series.
